Znc module
==========

Installs software and run a service using supervisor module under znc user id


Classes
-------

znc

    includes the following znc::package znc::user znc::service


znc::package

    installs znc and znc-extra package


znc::user

    creates a group and a user named znc


znc::service

    includes znc::service::supervisor

    You need to include supervisor


znc::service::supervisor

    creates a supervisor process to run znc with znc identity


